General.Name: AEWIN Technologies Co.Ltd.
General.Description: AEWIN Technologies Co.,Ltd. provides network platform products and solutions in Taiwan and internationally. The company offers network appliances; general purpose and edge computing servers, and workstation products; network expansion modules; and other modules, as well as provides ODM/OEM services. Its products are used for network computing, software-defined wide area network, network functions virtualization infrastructure, multi-access edge computing/edge AI, and 5G/vRAN applications. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
